issio Moscovitica: The Role of the Jesuits in the Westernization of Russia, 1582–1689\" (1995) 255 pp.\nBULLET::::- Wright, Jonathan. \"From Immolation to Restoration: The Jesuits, 1773–1814.\" \"Theological Studies\" (2014) 75#4 pp. 729–745.\n\nBULLET::::- Cushner, Nicholas P. \"Soldiers of God: The Jesuits in Colonial America, 1565–1767\" (2002) 402 pp.\nBULLET::::- Garraghan, Gilbert J. \"The Jesuits Of The Middle United States\" (3 vol 1938) covers Midwest from 1800 to 1919 vol 1 online, ; vol 2; vol 3\nBULLET::::- McDonough, Peter. \"Men astutely trained : a history of the Jesuits in the American century\" (1994), covers 1900 to 1960s; online free\nBULLET::::- Schroth, Raymond A. \"The American Jesuits: A History\" (2009)\n\nBULLET::::- Desideri, Ippolito. \"Mission to Tibet: The Extraordinary Eighteenth-Century Account of Father Ippolito Desideri.\" Translated by Michael J. Sweet. Edited by Leonard Zwilling. Boston: Wisdom Publications, 2010.\nBULLET::::- Donnelly, John Patrick, ed. \"Jesuit Writings of the Early Modern Period: 1540–1640\" (2006)\n\nBULLET::::- Klaus Schatz. \"Geschichte der deutschen Jesuiten: Bd. 1: 1814–1872\" Münster: Aschendorff Verlag, 2013. XXX, 274 S. . online review\nBULLET::::- Schatz. \"Geschichte der deutschen Jesuiten: Bd. 2: 1872–1917\"\nBULLET::::- Schatz. \"Geschichte der deutschen Jesuiten: Bd. 3: 1917–1945\"\nBULLET::::- Schatz. \"Geschichte der deutschen Jesuiten: Bd. 4: 1945–1983\"\nBULLET::::- Schatz. \"Geschichte der deutschen Jesuiten: Bd. 5: Quellen, Glossar, Biogramme, Gesamtregister\"\n\nBULLET::::- Benedict XVI's Address to the Members of the Society of Jesus, 22 April 2006\nBULLET::::- Benedict XVI's Visit to the Pontifical Gregorian University, 3 November 2006\n\nBULLET::::- The Jesuit Ratio Studiorum of 1599\nBULLET::::- The Jesuit Mission Press in Japan, 1591–1610\nBULLET::::- Letter of the Jesuit Social Justice Secretariat to the leaders of the G8, July 2005\nBULLET::::- The Spiritual Exercises of St. Ignatius o